<paragraph blockId="178.[151,1437,151,1112]" box="[199,947,151,176]" pageId="178" pageNumber="179">
<emphasis box="[199,279,152,175]" italics="true" pageId="178" pageNumber="179">Queen.</emphasis>
Similar to workers but slightly larger, alate and with ocelli.
